<TITLE>
Apotamkin, the Real Story
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the real Native American mythological figure Apotamkin,
a fanged sea monster from the folklore of the Maliseet and Passamaquoddy tribes.">
